Advertising Principles
No Third-Party Advertisements or Analytics:
The Starry Stories app is dedicated to providing a safe and distraction-free environment for children. As part of our commitment to child safety, we do not include any third-party advertisements or analytics within our app. This ensures that the personal data and privacy of our young users are protected, aligning with our goal to offer a secure and enjoyable experience for children.
Collecting and Using Your Personal Data
Starry Stories rigorously adheres to all applicable privacy laws and regulations, including the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA), the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), and other relevant child protection legislations. We ensure that our app delivers valuable functionality and entertainment for users of all ages, while strictly respecting the privacy and data protection requirements specific to children. Our app includes a privacy policy that comprehensively covers our data handling practices, ensuring transparency and compliance with all child privacy statutes.
Additionally, to fully align with the guidelines, it is important to emphasize that the app includes features or content that provide value regardless of age, and that any data collection for compliance with legal requirements is done behind a parental gate to ensure safety and compliance with children’s privacy laws.
Data collection within the Starry Stories app is conducted solely from adults who have provided explicit consent, and none of the requested data is mandatory, ensuring respect for user preferences and privacy rights.
